{"tid":1432251,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好心你班人唔好持住自己有充份理由 就做咩都正確啦","createTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T17:04:43.000Z","uid":25168,"like":20,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9d4979584faa332d0b03c8db9dd91d35fa5535c9","tid":1432251,"uid":25168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:48:16.000Z","msg":"鐘樓單野怪成咁<br />\n思考下都知唔係我地做<br />\n但見到成堆人係度話 黑衫點點點 好過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢d人都算啦 當佢無腦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1Ao3wW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1Ao3wW.png&h=6bb8c0b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到有條友話 &lsquo;示威者持住自己有充份理由 就做咩都正確&rsquo;<br />\n最撚好笑既係禁入去佢地既profile<br />\n見到佢平時係係咁share支持反送中既post <br />\n唔撚係藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZZr0mhk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZZr0mhk.png&h=40f2b871&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好心用下腦 唔好講埋d弱智說話啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母就算真係我地呢邊做<br />\n咪幫佢補穫囉<br />\n仲係度踩多腳 割蓆割唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"014efbf076442ac5c6633e36e4a9aae5cdbbc677","tid":1432251,"uid":25168,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-08T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"如果見到你地識既人有呢種弱智<br />\n唔該大大力屌醒佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1.用下腦諗下會唔會係對家抹黑<br />\n（幾撚時見到有人噴 一派胡言/五十不變）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n似大陸人 